                                    </p>
                                    <p align="left" class="article-title"><singleline label="Title"><%= link_to "NI #{@issue.number} - #{@issue.title}", issue_url(@issue) %></singleline></p>
                                    <div align="left" class="article-content">
                                        <multiline label="Description">Hi [salutation],<br /><br />
                                        Thanks very much for your interest in the New Internationalist. We've just published the <%= link_to "#{@issue.release.strftime("%B")} issue", issue_url(@issue) %> of New Internationalist magazine. If you <a href="https://digital.newint.com.au/users/sign_up">sign up</a> and take out a subscription you'll be able to read it right away. We're an independent publisher so we'd very much appreciate your support.</multiline>
                                        <% if not @issue.email_text.blank? %><br /><multiline><%= simple_format @issue.email_text %></multiline><% end %>
                                    </div>
                                </td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr><td class="w580" width="580" height="10"></td></tr>
                        </tbody></table>
                    </layout>

                    <hr />

                    <layout label="Text with right-aligned image">
